- To compile all the exercises at once:
      Use the command: make

- To compile one specific exercise (e.g., exo3):
      Use the command: make exo3

- To execute a compiled exercise (e.g., exo3):
      Use the command: ./exo3

- To delete all compiled executables:
      Use the command: make clean

- To delete a specific executable (e.g., exo3):
      Use the command: rm -f exo3
